<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ العصر<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٧٧:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {وَالْعَصْرِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> إِنَّ الْإِنْسَانَ لَفِي خُسْرٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> إِلَّا الَّذِينَ آمَنُوا وَعَمِلُوا الصَّالِحَاتِ وَتَوَاصَوْا بِالْحَقِّ وَتَوَاصَوْا بِالصَّبْرِ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>} <span class="c4">[العصر: ١ - ٣]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ يَحْيَى:</span> العَصْرُ: الدَّهْرُ، أَقْسَمَ بِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص١٣١:</span> <span class="c3">{خُسْرٍ}</span>: <span class="c2">«ضَلاَلٍ،<span class="c5"> ثُمَّ اسْتَثْنَى:</span> إِلَّا مَنْ آمَنَ»</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>